questionsAndAnswers.question: What do I need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You need to provide me with hosting information/ WordPress login information, your logo, an outline of your website ( rough sketch or mockup design), and content for your website including text,, images, videos, etc…

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide only Fixing issues service?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I do. You can contact me directly for a discussion.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is the staging site accepted?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, the staging site accepted to create the site first on staging and then free migration to the live site (Not in Basic Plan Order)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do I need to provide Responsive Design?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Ideally, yes but if you don't have a responsive design, I will make the design fully responsive.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I have a different number of pages than listed in the gig? or I have custom requirements?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No worries! Just contact me directly and I can create a special order package for you at a suitable price.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I clone my "X" website to WordPress?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! I am also capable of converting existing websites to WordPress. Please contact me beforehand so I can take a look! Then we can make a special custom offer for this.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I easily modify the content or images on the site after it has been created?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you can edit everything very easily using the builder. If you want then I can guide you in a quick meeting or send you a video.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How many plugins you'll be using?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: It depends on your functional requirements. However, we use less plugin unless it's important.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you give support after-sales service?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I always strive to create long-term, ongoing customer relationships.
